---
/**
 * Features Section — 6 张功能卡片
 */
---

<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-badge">
        <i data-lucide="layers" class="icon-xs"></i>
        Core Features
      </span>
      <h2>Comprehensive Sunrise & Sunset Analytics for Every City</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">From golden hour precision to moon phase tracking, SunriseTime covers every data point photographers, travelers, and communities need to plan their day perfectly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-sunrise">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-sunrise">
          <i data-lucide="sunrise" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Precision Sunrise & Sunset</h3>
        <p>Accurate to within 1 minute using the NOAA Solar Calculator. Get civil, nautical, and astronomical twilight times for any city on any date.</p>
        <a href="#dashboard" class="feature-link" aria-label="See sunrise and sunset data">
          Explore data
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-golden">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-golden">
          <i data-lucide="camera" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Golden Hour Tracking</h3>
        <p>Never miss the perfect light again. Get precise morning and evening golden hour windows, plus blue hour timing for stunning landscape and portrait photography.</p>
        <a href="#dashboard" class="feature-link" aria-label="See golden hour features">
          Plan your shoot
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-moon">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-moon">
          <i data-lucide="moon" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Moon Phase & Illumination</h3>
        <p>Track current moon phase, illumination percentage, moonrise and moonset times. Plan night photography sessions and astronomy activities with confidence.</p>
        <a href="#dashboard" class="feature-link" aria-label="See moon phase features">
          View moon data
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-prayer">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-prayer">
          <i data-lucide="clock" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Prayer Time Calculator</h3>
        <p>Accurate Islamic prayer times calculated using multiple juristic methods. Supports Fajr, Dhuhr, Asr, Maghrib, and Isha with customizable calculation standards.</p>
        <a href="#dashboard" class="feature-link" aria-label="See prayer time features">
          Check times
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-daylight">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-daylight">
          <i data-lucide="bar-chart-3" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Daylight Trend Analytics</h3>
        <p>Visualize how daylight hours change across seasons with interactive charts. Compare daylight trends between cities and track solstice and equinox events.</p>
        <a href="#dashboard" class="feature-link" aria-label="See daylight analytics">
          See trends
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-speed">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-speed">
          <i data-lucide="gauge" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Edge-Powered Performance</h3>
        <p>Deployed on Cloudflare's 300+ global edge nodes with KV caching. Every request served in under 50ms — faster than any competitor in the sunrise data space.</p>
        <a href="#dashboard" class="feature-link" aria-label="See performance details">
          See benchmarks
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
